{"tid":1280971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【被捕唔等如坐監】嚴正警告：入到狗屋，乜鳩都唔好講","createTime":"2019-07-03T06:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T03:16:11.000Z","uid":64981,"like":200,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"17d4cc6847d4b1e71bafe420585d36951640d9fa","tid":1280971,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:48:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">學能大神緊急呼籲：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/63rKrhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F63rKrhW.png&h=b6783f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">懶人包：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 乜鳩都唔好講<br />\n2. 講任何嘢都會容易啲入罪，所以乜鳩都唔好講<br />\n3. 講錯少少嘢都可能變不誠實證人，所以乜鳩都唔好講<br />\n4. 除左嗌肚餓，乜鳩都唔好講</span><br />\n<br />\n最好當然要記得義務律師電話，到時搵人幫，但總括而言：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">乜鳩都唔好講，呢個係你嘅權利</span>"},{"pid":"baf84f67e47465108ddfd505347d0c19dca8fb0f","tid":1280971,"uid":44646,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:49:46.000Z","msg":"可以要求睇醫生<br />\n去醫院坐會舒服少少"},{"pid":"457c28910ed7ea4d5341501676642db1021dd248","tid":1280971,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9396f6e3d6054058a0b0c9f57d376dafe8b7e4","tid":1280971,"uid":64981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:50:14.000Z","msg":"幫手share俾自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做好法律武裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c1c06ae95ad7beedd464c54bad874ddf8cccd7","tid":1280971,"uid":64981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:51:21.000Z","msg":"未雨綢繆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知會唔會有